Implemented a deterministic cue/weighting refinement for the modal compiler registry lane, focused on the requested family-conflict pairs.

**Code changes**
- Expanded temporal cue coverage with explicit deadline phrases (`not later than`, `no later than`) in [modal_registry.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-dedup-8codex-gpu-1h-20260518T233253Z-codex-compiler_registry-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-02-packet-000021-20260518_235032/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/modal_registry.py:270).
- Added conditional-procedural cues for hearing-gated norms (`after/upon/on notice and opportunity for hearing`, including reasonable-notice variants) in [modal_registry.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-dedup-8codex-gpu-1h-20260518T233253Z-codex-compiler_registry-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-02-packet-000021-20260518_235032/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/modal_registry.py:327).
- Added statutory frame cue phrases (`under this section`, `under this chapter`) in [modal_registry.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-dedup-8codex-gpu-1h-20260518T233253Z-codex-compiler_registry-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-02-packet-000021-20260518_235032/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/modal_registry.py:366).
- Tightened temporal `after` extraction so it only counts when local context is time-like (deadline/sequence context), plus helper lookbehind scan, in [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-dedup-8codex-gpu-1h-20260518T233253Z-codex-compiler_registry-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-02-packet-000021-20260518_235032/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:620).
- Extended deontic competing-scope soft-cap to include conditional competition, with a stricter conditional-only cap, in [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-dedup-8codex-gpu-1h-20260518T233253Z-codex-compiler_registry-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-02-packet-000021-20260518_235032/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:1206).
- Added corresponding conditional scope phrases and generic-frame debias term coverage in [spacy_modal_codec.py](/home/barberb/portland-laws.github.io/workspace/codex-work/uscode-modal-vector-dedup-8codex-gpu-1h-20260518T233253Z-codex-compiler_registry-02/worktrees/agent-codex-compiler_registry-02-packet-000021-20260518_235032/ipfs_datasets_py/optimizers/logic_theorem_optimizer/spacy_modal_codec.py:33).

